      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Looks a match race again. ZEWINNA (2) kept finding but just failed on the post when runner-up behind HURRICANE KETUT last time. Meets that galloper better at the weights and gets a chance to turn the tables. Hard to knock the form of HURRICANE KETUT (1) though winning three of the last four starts. Kept coming to score latest over ZEWINNA and despite more weight will be tough to stop again. LONTANO (4) was a close-up third two back then ran well below expectations in the latest. Gets a chance to bounce back. RICH CLAN (5) is another better than last run and gets his chance to atone. JUST A NEEDS (3) is sure to be thereabouts.",
